<h1>1 Patay, 1 Gindis-armahan sang NPA sa Central Negros</h1>
<p>Author: Philippine Revolution Web Central</p>
<p>Publish Time: 2023-02-24T99:00:00-04:00</p>
<p>Modified Time: None</p>
<p>Description: Ginadayaw sang Leonardo Panaligan Command-New People’s Army ang pursigido nga pagpatuman sang mga desisyon sang Rebolusyonaryong Korte sang Pumuluyo matapos ang pagvista kag pagpamatbat sanday Nolet</p>
<p>Images: ['<a href="https://philippinerevolution.nu/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/npa-central-negros-map-1024x576.png">npa-central-negros-map-1024x576.png</a>']</p>
